    <title>Manage legend sets</title>
    <para>You can create your own legend sets to ensure meaningful maps. </para>
    <note>
        <para>Continuous legends are supposed to end and start on the same value, for example 0-50
            and 50-80. The GIS app automatically take care of
            <?oxy_comment_start author="Home" timestamp="20160413T120439+0200" comment="Of what?"?>this<?oxy_comment_end?>.
